data.description: Take a look at this South Sound slice of heaven offering 5.18 acres of bliss in a gated & exclusive enclave known as Whiskey Beach Estates. Dappled with striking Madronas & native evergreens, this lot gently cascades into a westerly slope offering multiple creative options to frame the filtered water and mountain views.  The community is served by two, shared wells, and power is onsite.  Lots of legwork completed! Approved septic plans and geo-tech studies included. 320' of private beach overlooks the Puget Sound, offering panoramic views of the Olympic Mountains to the northwest.  The lot is conveniently bisected by a private road, offering a prime investment for those wishing to subdivide in the future. Buyer to do due diligence.
